WEBVTT

00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:02.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ONE YEAR AGO</b></Default>

00:00:02.209 --> 00:00:04.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm moving!
I wanted to tell you in person.</b></Default>

00:00:05.009 --> 00:00:06.089 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Where to?</b></Default>

00:00:06.169 --> 00:00:07.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- To Okinawa.</b></Default>

00:00:07.469 --> 00:00:08.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I'm in a warmer area</b></Default>

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it isn't as hard for my body
to keep going.</b></Default>

00:00:11.550 --> 00:00:12.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After I get settled in</b></Default>

00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:14.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you and Mai
should come visit me.</b></Default>

00:00:14.349 --> 00:00:16.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Okinawa, huh?
Sounds great.</b></Default>

00:00:17.140 --> 00:00:19.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll send you a letter when
I get used to things over there.</b></Default>

00:00:20.149 --> 00:00:22.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'll be waiting.
You better send pictures, too.</b></Default>

00:00:22.809 --> 00:00:23.859 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes!</b></Default>

00:00:23.940 --> 00:00:26.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be sure to enclose
a swimsuit shot.</b></Default>

00:00:26.359 --> 00:00:28.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Please wait three years
to do that.</b></Default>

00:00:28.109 --> 00:00:29.489 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In three years, then.</b></Default>

00:00:29.910 --> 00:00:31.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll send you something in
the mail that'll make you have</b></Default>

00:00:31.949 --> 00:00:32.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a huge fight with Mai.</b></Default>

00:00:33.079 --> 00:00:34.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Looking forward to that.</b></Default>

00:00:34.490 --> 00:00:36.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yes!
Oh, yeah.</b></Default>

00:00:36.909 --> 00:00:40.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There was something else that I
thought I should bring up today.</b></Default>

00:00:40.670 --> 00:00:41.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

00:00:41.880 --> 00:00:44.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- There's something
slightly concerning.</b></Default>

00:00:44.380 --> 00:00:45.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's going on?</b></Default>

00:00:45.670 --> 00:00:48.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I can still
remember everything.</b></Default>

00:00:48.340 --> 00:00:50.719 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You and Mai don't
have those memories</b></Default>

00:00:50.799 --> 00:00:52.929 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it seems like
I retained everything.</b></Default>

00:00:53.350 --> 00:00:55.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can still remember memories
from every version</b></Default>

00:00:55.969 --> 00:00:59.479 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of myself that I've lived</b></Default>

00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:01.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, I already knew that.</b></Default>

00:01:01.689 --> 00:01:04.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But nothing I do can make
it show up.</b></Default>

00:01:04.519 --> 00:01:06.069 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's not showing up?</b></Default>

00:01:06.150 --> 00:01:07.359 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This doesn't.</b></Default>

00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:09.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TOUKO KIRISHIMA [SOCIAL WORLD] MUSIC VIDEO</b></Default>

00:01:09.239 --> 00:01:10.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's...</b></Default>

00:01:11.489 --> 00:01:14.319 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- In the multiple futures
that I have experienced...</b></Default>

00:01:14.909 --> 00:01:18.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Touko Kirishima's music
didn't exist in any of them.</b></Default>

00:01:19.040 --> 00:01:20.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [gasps]</b></Default>

00:01:21.540 --> 00:01:22.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see now.</b></Default>

00:01:22.790 --> 00:01:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what this is about.</b></Default>

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:25.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yep, that's what it's about.</b></Default>

00:01:25.670 --> 00:01:28.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, people do say every rose
has it's thorns, you know.</b></Default>

00:01:28.760 --> 00:01:30.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And from what I can tell</b></Default>

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:33.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're worried that your actions
in this world have changed</b></Default>

00:01:33.090 --> 00:01:34.969 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the world in the future.
Is that right?</b></Default>

00:01:35.349 --> 00:01:38.349 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh-huh, and I believe you're
my accomplice in that aspect.</b></Default>

00:01:38.599 --> 00:01:41.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you ask me, as long
as no one's faced misfortune</b></Default>

00:01:41.390 --> 00:01:43.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you can just leave things
the way they are.</b></Default>

00:01:43.560 --> 00:01:44.689 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At the very least</b></Default>

00:01:44.769 --> 00:01:46.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Touko Kirishima's gaining
something from it</b></Default>

00:01:47.069 --> 00:01:48.439 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since she's going viral.</b></Default>

00:01:48.530 --> 00:01:50.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You mean I should stop
worrying about others</b></Default>

00:01:50.609 --> 00:01:52.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and enjoy life to make up
for all the time</b></Default>

00:01:52.530 --> 00:01:53.989 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I spent being sick, right?</b></Default>

00:01:54.069 --> 00:01:56.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, exactly.
- But I am enjoying life.</b></Default>

00:01:56.989 --> 00:01:59.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like today I'm having
a huge parfait</b></Default>

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that I've been dying for.</b></Default>

00:02:00.409 --> 00:02:01.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's so small.</b></Default>

00:02:01.709 --> 00:02:03.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, if I'm able
to feel genuine happiness</b></Default>

00:02:03.750 --> 00:02:05.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the little things</b></Default>

00:02:05.129 --> 00:02:07.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I ought to be
the happiest person around.</b></Default>

00:02:07.840 --> 00:02:09.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You do have a point there.</b></Default>

00:02:10.960 --> 00:02:12.469 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa!</b></Default>

00:02:14.180 --> 00:02:15.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh?</b></Default>

00:02:15.719 --> 00:02:17.349 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How long you gonna sleep for?</b></Default>

00:02:17.430 --> 00:02:19.139 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, man.
Class is over.</b></Default>

00:02:21.310 --> 00:02:24.229 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic piano music]</b></Default>

00:02:24.310 --> 00:02:31.319 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

00:02:31.939 --> 00:02:33.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [yawns]</b></Default>

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:36.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SEPTEMBER 30TH</b></Default>

00:02:36.370 --> 00:02:37.569 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]
SEPTEMBER 30TH</b></Default>

00:02:37.569 --> 00:02:39.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SEPTEMBER 30TH</b></Default>

00:02:39.620 --> 00:02:42.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Conton Candy's "Snow Drop"]</b></Default>

00:02:42.620 --> 00:02:49.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

00:02:49.919 --> 00:02:52.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:02:52.919 --> 00:02:59.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

00:03:28.580 --> 00:03:35.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

00:03:47.199 --> 00:03:53.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:04:03.909 --> 00:04:09.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

00:04:13.090 --> 00:04:16.339 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- To be an adult.
What does it mean to become one?</b></Default>

00:04:17.259 --> 00:04:20.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, are you still
the same person as back then?</b></Default>

00:04:21.800 --> 00:04:24.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And cut there!
We're all clear!</b></Default>

00:04:25.519 --> 00:04:27.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, there.
We just finished filming.</b></Default>

00:04:27.639 --> 00:04:29.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thanks for your hard work</b></Default>

00:04:29.639 --> 00:04:32.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, what time do you think
you'll be home today?</b></Default>

00:04:32.149 --> 00:04:35.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Actually, Fukuyama invited me
to a get-together</b></Default>

00:04:35.110 --> 00:04:38.319 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the new student orientation
so I won't be back till later.</b></Default>

00:04:38.399 --> 00:04:39.399 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmph.</b></Default>

00:04:39.490 --> 00:04:41.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- By the way</b></Default>

00:04:41.360 --> 00:04:42.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Toyohama and Hirokawa?</b></Default>

00:04:42.819 --> 00:04:44.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, I do!
- No, we can't.</b></Default>

00:04:44.279 --> 00:04:46.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have a concert rehearsal.
- Oh, that's right!</b></Default>

00:04:46.949 --> 00:04:49.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We've barely seen each other
all summer</b></Default>

00:04:49.160 --> 00:04:51.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we finally have a chance
for the first time in a month</b></Default>

00:04:51.790 --> 00:04:53.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you're blowing me off?</b></Default>

00:04:53.209 --> 00:04:55.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know, Mai, I worked hard
to go to your university</b></Default>

00:04:55.750 --> 00:04:58.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but I never imagined how little
I'd be able to see you.</b></Default>

00:04:58.509 --> 00:05:00.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So if you tell me not to go</b></Default>

00:05:00.879 --> 00:05:02.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, it's okay.</b></Default>

00:05:02.339 --> 00:05:05.509 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides, even if I leave now</b></Default>

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:07.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So go ahead and have fun
with your friend.</b></Default>

00:05:07.850 --> 00:05:10.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then I'll take you up
on your kind offer.</b></Default>

00:05:10.100 --> 00:05:11.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hopefully you find
a cute girl there</b></Default>

00:05:11.939 --> 00:05:13.149 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who's just your type.</b></Default>

00:05:13.519 --> 00:05:15.189 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, I'm looking forward
to that.</b></Default>

00:05:15.269 --> 00:05:17.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I won't forgive you
if you cheat on me.</b></Default>

00:05:20.029 --> 00:05:22.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train speeding up]</b></Default>

00:05:22.779 --> 00:05:25.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:05:25.529 --> 00:05:28.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Mai Sakurajima</b></Default>

00:05:28.199 --> 00:05:30.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so jealous.</b></Default>

00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:31.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all laughing]</b></Default>

00:05:31.920 --> 00:05:33.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing continues]</b></Default>

00:05:34.329 --> 00:05:37.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Two hours of all you can drink
for 1</b></Default>

00:05:37.879 --> 00:05:40.839 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd say a two-liter bottle costs
200 yen.</b></Default>

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:43.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can make my money's worth
if I drink 11 more liters.</b></Default>

00:05:44.050 --> 00:05:45.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- May I sit here?</b></Default>

00:05:46.100 --> 00:05:48.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Honestly, I'd prefer
if you didn't.</b></Default>

00:05:48.269 --> 00:05:50.889 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What? And why's that.
- Oh, you know.</b></Default>

00:05:50.980 --> 00:05:53.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because of the death glares
from across the room.</b></Default>

00:05:53.189 --> 00:05:54.189 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm?</b></Default>

00:05:54.980 --> 00:05:58.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seemed like they were about
to trade user Ids, so--</b></Default>

00:05:58.360 --> 00:06:00.899 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you don't want to</b></Default>

00:06:00.990 --> 00:06:03.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, normally I would say no.</b></Default>

00:06:03.110 --> 00:06:05.569 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But for some reason
it's not normal?</b></Default>

00:06:05.660 --> 00:06:07.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't have a smartphone.</b></Default>

00:06:07.490 --> 00:06:09.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That is unusual.</b></Default>

00:06:09.370 --> 00:06:11.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, so nobody ever
believes me.</b></Default>

00:06:11.870 --> 00:06:12.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did you get frustrated</b></Default>

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:14.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and throw your smartphone
into the ocean?</b></Default>

00:06:14.790 --> 00:06:16.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Do people actually do that?</b></Default>

00:06:17.420 --> 00:06:18.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

00:06:18.589 --> 00:06:20.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a freshman
in statistical science.</b></Default>

00:06:20.839 --> 00:06:23.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta Azusagawa.
- Why the introduction?</b></Default>

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:25.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Isn't that what these
get-togethers are for?</b></Default>

00:06:26.009 --> 00:06:27.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, then let's cheers.</b></Default>

00:06:27.800 --> 00:06:29.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm an international
commerce major.</b></Default>

00:06:29.930 --> 00:06:31.389 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Miori Mito.</b></Default>

00:06:31.470 --> 00:06:33.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A pleasure.
[glasses clink]</b></Default>

00:06:33.769 --> 00:06:35.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, to be honest</b></Default>

00:06:35.439 --> 00:06:37.519 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I already knew who you were</b></Default>

00:06:37.610 --> 00:06:39.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I am a celebrity, after all.</b></Default>

00:06:39.860 --> 00:06:42.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Although, the one who's
actually famous</b></Default>

00:06:42.189 --> 00:06:44.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is Mai Sakurajima
and not you.</b></Default>

00:06:44.949 --> 00:06:48.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, to have a beautiful
significant other of my own.</b></Default>

00:06:48.199 --> 00:06:49.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mmm, tasty.</b></Default>

00:06:49.949 --> 00:06:52.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Azusagawa</b></Default>

00:06:52.500 --> 00:06:54.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mainly to eat some food.</b></Default>

00:06:54.209 --> 00:06:55.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The other tables have lots
of people</b></Default>

00:06:55.750 --> 00:06:57.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so there's fewer servings
for me.</b></Default>

00:06:57.420 --> 00:06:59.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Everyone must be starving.</b></Default>

00:06:59.379 --> 00:07:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Does that mean
you aren't Mito?</b></Default>

00:07:01.339 --> 00:07:03.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Actually, I'm starving
as well.</b></Default>

00:07:03.379 --> 00:07:06.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Time's almost up now</b></Default>

00:07:06.509 --> 00:07:09.139 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The after party's karaoke</b></Default>

00:07:09.220 --> 00:07:11.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hmm.
- After party.</b></Default>

00:07:11.310 --> 00:07:12.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, I'm not a singer.</b></Default>

00:07:12.889 --> 00:07:14.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you going, Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:17.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh-uh. Someone's waiting
for me at home.</b></Default>

00:07:18.980 --> 00:07:20.939 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're okay leaving your
friend behind like that?</b></Default>

00:07:21.019 --> 00:07:23.439 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Who, Manami?
- If that's her name, sure.</b></Default>

00:07:23.990 --> 00:07:25.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's fine.</b></Default>

00:07:25.360 --> 00:07:27.569 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I stayed any longer</b></Default>

00:07:27.660 --> 00:07:28.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I see.</b></Default>

00:07:28.819 --> 00:07:29.779 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Must be rough when the guy</b></Default>

00:07:29.870 --> 00:07:31.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your friend wants wants you.</b></Default>

00:07:31.329 --> 00:07:33.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm surprised you noticed.</b></Default>

00:07:33.579 --> 00:07:35.709 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, that's right.
Here.</b></Default>

00:07:35.790 --> 00:07:38.629 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If my breath stinks</b></Default>

00:07:38.709 --> 00:07:41.209 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That fried chicken
we ate had garlic in it.</b></Default>

00:07:41.290 --> 00:07:43.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you're about to see
your girlfriend, right?</b></Default>

00:07:43.459 --> 00:07:45.089 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thanks for looking out.</b></Default>

00:07:46.379 --> 00:07:48.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chomps]</b></Default>

00:07:49.050 --> 00:07:51.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I don't wanna
seem ungrateful</b></Default>

00:07:51.680 --> 00:07:54.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you probably shouldn't
do stuff like that for guys.</b></Default>

00:07:54.850 --> 00:07:56.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why's that?
- 'Cause it seems like you don't</b></Default>

00:07:56.939 --> 00:07:59.189 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>want guys after you.
- Oh, it's all right.</b></Default>

00:07:59.269 --> 00:08:01.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll only do something
like that to you.</b></Default>

00:08:01.110 --> 00:08:03.399 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Am I being targeted
or something?</b></Default>

00:08:03.480 --> 00:08:05.069 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- 'Cause it's different
with you.</b></Default>

00:08:05.149 --> 00:08:07.319 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know I'll be fine because
you'd never end up falling</b></Default>

00:08:07.399 --> 00:08:08.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in love with me.</b></Default>

00:08:08.449 --> 00:08:09.529 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, you already have</b></Default>

00:08:09.610 --> 00:08:11.069 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the cutest girlfriend in Japan.</b></Default>

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:12.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you meant to say
the cutest girlfriend</b></Default>

00:08:13.029 --> 00:08:14.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the world</b></Default>

00:08:14.790 --> 00:08:17.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Wow, so humble.
- Here you go, sir.</b></Default>

00:08:17.790 --> 00:08:19.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you don't mind.
- Nobody's taking them.</b></Default>

00:08:19.959 --> 00:08:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Seems that way.</b></Default>

00:08:21.079 --> 00:08:22.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I know it might sound
a bit weird</b></Default>

00:08:22.959 --> 00:08:25.959 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but maybe that woman
is only visible to you and me.</b></Default>

00:08:26.050 --> 00:08:27.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That can't be.
- You don't know?</b></Default>

00:08:27.800 --> 00:08:29.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They call it puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

00:08:29.970 --> 00:08:32.509 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>People becoming invisible</b></Default>

00:08:32.600 --> 00:08:34.429 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and splitting into two bodies.</b></Default>

00:08:34.509 --> 00:08:36.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It can be all sorts of things.</b></Default>

00:08:36.429 --> 00:08:37.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Really?</b></Default>

00:08:37.929 --> 00:08:40.519 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If you wouldn't mind, please.
Thank you so much!</b></Default>

00:08:41.399 --> 00:08:43.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you!
Have a nice day!</b></Default>

00:08:43.440 --> 00:08:45.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Seems like others can see her</b></Default>

00:08:45.649 --> 00:08:46.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Guess so.
- Thank you so much!</b></Default>

00:08:46.899 --> 00:08:48.899 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Anyways, isn't that lady
too old</b></Default>

00:08:48.990 --> 00:08:50.529 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to be going through puberty?</b></Default>

00:08:50.610 --> 00:08:52.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, are you going
through puberty?</b></Default>

00:08:52.740 --> 00:08:55.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I would like to graduate
from it soon.</b></Default>

00:08:55.200 --> 00:08:56.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How 'bout you?</b></Default>

00:08:56.539 --> 00:08:59.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think I"m probably still in
the middle of it.</b></Default>

00:08:59.539 --> 00:09:00.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why's that?</b></Default>

00:09:00.669 --> 00:09:02.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- 'Cause I've never had
a boyfriend.</b></Default>

00:09:02.379 --> 00:09:04.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That tracks.
- Wow.</b></Default>

00:09:04.460 --> 00:09:07.509 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A taken guy looking down on me.
How infuriating.</b></Default>

00:09:07.590 --> 00:09:08.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:09:08.840 --> 00:09:10.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna shop
a little before I head home.</b></Default>

00:09:10.549 --> 00:09:12.179 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you around.</b></Default>

00:09:14.350 --> 00:09:15.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's been
a while since I heard</b></Default>

00:09:15.850 --> 00:09:17.639 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the words "puberty syndrome."</b></Default>

00:09:20.730 --> 00:09:21.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door unlocking]</b></Default>

00:09:22.059 --> 00:09:23.809 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, I'm home, Nasuno.</b></Default>

00:09:23.899 --> 00:09:25.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:09:26.360 --> 00:09:28.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Welcome home, Sakuta.
- Hi, Mai.</b></Default>

00:09:29.490 --> 00:09:30.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And welcome home to you.</b></Default>

00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:32.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Thank you.</b></Default>

00:09:32.950 --> 00:09:33.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

00:09:33.990 --> 00:09:35.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you staring
at me like that?</b></Default>

00:09:35.580 --> 00:09:38.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, it is the first time in
a month that I've seen you.</b></Default>

00:09:38.450 --> 00:09:40.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I was basking in your beauty.</b></Default>

00:09:40.500 --> 00:09:41.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Happy, huh?</b></Default>

00:09:42.710 --> 00:09:44.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exciting musical sting]
- Question!</b></Default>

00:09:44.169 --> 00:09:46.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A building in Barcelona designed
by Antonio Gaudi</b></Default>

00:09:47.049 --> 00:09:50.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is still under construction
after 130 years.</b></Default>

00:09:50.299 --> 00:09:51.929 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yokohama Station!</b></Default>

00:09:52.009 --> 00:09:54.679 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crowd laughing]
- Oh, welcome home, big brother.</b></Default>

00:09:54.759 --> 00:09:56.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You're here, too, Kaede?</b></Default>

00:09:56.389 --> 00:09:59.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I called to let you know
'cause I have work tomorrow.</b></Default>

00:09:59.100 --> 00:10:02.139 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Big brother, you really need
to get a smartphone.</b></Default>

00:10:02.230 --> 00:10:04.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, Kaede</b></Default>

00:10:04.440 --> 00:10:06.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to hear those words come out
of your mouth.</b></Default>

00:10:06.309 --> 00:10:07.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Don't you agree, Mai?</b></Default>

00:10:07.519 --> 00:10:08.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'd be better for you, too</b></Default>

00:10:08.570 --> 00:10:09.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if he had a smartphone, right?</b></Default>

00:10:10.029 --> 00:10:11.779 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I think I've gotten used
to it.</b></Default>

00:10:12.200 --> 00:10:14.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You can't let Mai coddle
you forever, you know.</b></Default>

00:10:15.240 --> 00:10:16.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna take a bath first.</b></Default>

00:10:18.539 --> 00:10:19.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

00:10:19.659 --> 00:10:22.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sakuta, did you eat
a proper dinner?</b></Default>

00:10:22.370 --> 00:10:24.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mainly some fried chicken
and beans.</b></Default>

00:10:24.539 --> 00:10:27.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And did you see any cute girls
that were your type?</b></Default>

00:10:27.169 --> 00:10:28.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I did not.</b></Default>

00:10:28.500 --> 00:10:30.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, isn't that a shame?
- Oh, but--</b></Default>

00:10:30.799 --> 00:10:32.799 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- But what?
Was there a girl?</b></Default>

00:10:32.879 --> 00:10:33.929 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, actually.</b></Default>

00:10:34.009 --> 00:10:35.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One who doesn't have
a smartphone.</b></Default>

00:10:35.799 --> 00:10:37.139 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Good joke.</b></Default>

00:10:37.220 --> 00:10:39.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The punch line isn't that
only you can see her, is it?</b></Default>

00:10:40.519 --> 00:10:41.889 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm not exactly sure</b></Default>

00:10:41.980 --> 00:10:44.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'll confirm on campus
next week and get back to you.</b></Default>

00:10:45.059 --> 00:10:48.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh. Well, it's getting late</b></Default>

00:10:48.110 --> 00:10:49.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Huh? Already?</b></Default>

00:10:49.440 --> 00:10:50.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I have an early morning.</b></Default>

00:10:51.190 --> 00:10:53.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll see you on campus
on Wednesday, 'kay?</b></Default>

00:10:53.649 --> 00:10:55.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Let me walk down with you.</b></Default>

00:10:55.360 --> 00:10:57.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Someone might take a photo</b></Default>

00:10:58.240 --> 00:11:00.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My agency is
a bit strict lately.</b></Default>

00:11:00.950 --> 00:11:02.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

00:11:02.120 --> 00:11:03.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, what are you doing?</b></Default>

00:11:04.830 --> 00:11:06.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, nothing much.</b></Default>

00:11:06.460 --> 00:11:07.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Goodbye, now.</b></Default>

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:10.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [chuckles]</b></Default>

00:11:11.450 --> 00:11:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>OCTOBER 3RD
YOKOHAMA CITY UNIVERSITY</b></Default>

00:11:14.759 --> 00:11:16.009 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mind if I sit here?</b></Default>

00:11:16.090 --> 00:11:17.889 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I would prefer if you didn't.</b></Default>

00:11:17.970 --> 00:11:19.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm sitting here anyway.</b></Default>

00:11:19.679 --> 00:11:21.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know, there are plenty
of other open seats.</b></Default>

00:11:22.059 --> 00:11:24.309 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, I looked around
and you were the only person</b></Default>

00:11:24.389 --> 00:11:25.309 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew in here.</b></Default>

00:11:25.389 --> 00:11:26.639 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then you should have chosen</b></Default>

00:11:26.730 --> 00:11:28.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a class that you could take
with your friends.</b></Default>

00:11:28.809 --> 00:11:30.059 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

00:11:30.149 --> 00:11:32.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think I have friends.</b></Default>

00:11:33.029 --> 00:11:35.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, you're making a
"This girl's trouble" face.</b></Default>

00:11:35.779 --> 00:11:38.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This is my, "She's trouble
and a pain in the butt" face.</b></Default>

00:11:39.200 --> 00:11:41.779 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Apparently my friends
are planning to set up</b></Default>

00:11:41.870 --> 00:11:44.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a matchmaking party
for my poor boyfriendless self.</b></Default>

00:11:44.750 --> 00:11:47.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why don't you just say</b></Default>

00:11:47.330 --> 00:11:49.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you can meet handsome guys</b></Default>

00:11:49.500 --> 00:11:51.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I keep that part to myself.</b></Default>

00:11:51.090 --> 00:11:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A mixer?
Can I go with you?</b></Default>

00:11:53.340 --> 00:11:55.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- A mixer isn't really a place
for an idol.</b></Default>

00:11:56.009 --> 00:11:57.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, yeah. Hmm.</b></Default>

00:11:57.840 --> 00:12:00.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ooh, so is this your new
girlfriend, big brother?</b></Default>

00:12:00.139 --> 00:12:02.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No.
- I'm his potential friend.</b></Default>

00:12:02.179 --> 00:12:03.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Miori Mito.</b></Default>

00:12:03.309 --> 00:12:04.809 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Neat! I'm one of his friends</b></Default>

00:12:04.889 --> 00:12:06.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uzuki Hirokawa.</b></Default>

00:12:06.350 --> 00:12:08.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a statistical science major
just like Big Brother.</b></Default>

00:12:08.850 --> 00:12:10.519 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Why Big Brother?</b></Default>

00:12:10.610 --> 00:12:12.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, I guess because
he's Kaede's big brother.</b></Default>

00:12:13.320 --> 00:12:15.529 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Really? I didn't know you had
a little sister.</b></Default>

00:12:15.610 --> 00:12:18.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So then is your little sister
good friends with Hirokawa?</b></Default>

00:12:19.070 --> 00:12:20.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I wouldn't say
they're friends.</b></Default>

00:12:20.570 --> 00:12:22.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's more like a fan.
- Fan?</b></Default>

00:12:22.740 --> 00:12:26.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yep! Me and Nodoka--who's an
international education major--</b></Default>

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are in an idol group called
Sweet Bullet together.</b></Default>

00:12:28.580 --> 00:12:31.169 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have a live show next week
so please come by, Miorin!</b></Default>

00:12:31.250 --> 00:12:32.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, girls!</b></Default>

00:12:32.919 --> 00:12:35.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all giggling
and talking at once]</b></Default>

00:12:36.629 --> 00:12:38.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Miorin?</b></Default>

00:12:38.720 --> 00:12:41.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:12:44.470 --> 00:12:47.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, Azusagawa!
Hey, let's go get lunch!</b></Default>

00:12:47.350 --> 00:12:49.389 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
- Ciao.</b></Default>

00:12:51.149 --> 00:12:54.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[unsettling piano music]</b></Default>

00:12:54.149 --> 00:12:59.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

00:12:59.399 --> 00:13:01.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is that another acquaintance
of yours?</b></Default>

00:13:01.570 --> 00:13:04.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She was one of my classmates
in middle school.</b></Default>

00:13:04.120 --> 00:13:06.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Dang, man, you're popular
with all the cute girls.</b></Default>

00:13:06.580 --> 00:13:08.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm really not, though.</b></Default>

00:13:08.159 --> 00:13:10.419 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We met again during
the matriculation ceremony</b></Default>

00:13:10.500 --> 00:13:13.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and chatted for a while.
- I wanna eat a Yokoichi bowl!</b></Default>

00:13:13.169 --> 00:13:14.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Shall we head
to the cafeteria?</b></Default>

00:13:14.590 --> 00:13:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm-hmm!
Oh, my goodness!</b></Default>

00:13:16.340 --> 00:13:18.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I totally forgot I have
a photo shoot today!</b></Default>

00:13:18.379 --> 00:13:20.549 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I gotta go!
- Another fashion magazine?</b></Default>

00:13:20.629 --> 00:13:22.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yep, yep!
- The last one you did</b></Default>

00:13:22.179 --> 00:13:24.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was so cute.
- I'll totally get my own copy!</b></Default>

00:13:24.850 --> 00:13:27.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, me, too.
- Good luck with the shoot.</b></Default>

00:13:27.179 --> 00:13:28.679 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hasta mañana!</b></Default>

00:13:31.889 --> 00:13:32.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Where should we eat?</b></Default>

00:13:33.059 --> 00:13:34.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The school store?</b></Default>

00:13:34.309 --> 00:13:35.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I really only wanted
a sandwich</b></Default>

00:13:36.070 --> 00:13:37.529 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so that would be a lifesaver.</b></Default>

00:13:37.610 --> 00:13:39.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, I feel you on that one.</b></Default>

00:13:39.360 --> 00:13:40.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all giggling]</b></Default>

00:13:40.820 --> 00:13:43.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You know, girls can
really be super scary.</b></Default>

00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:45.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Isn't everybody like that?</b></Default>

00:13:46.779 --> 00:13:48.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, tell me!</b></Default>

00:13:48.289 --> 00:13:50.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What happened with Mito after
the party on Friday?</b></Default>

00:13:50.539 --> 00:13:52.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, not much. Why?</b></Default>

00:13:52.539 --> 00:13:53.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- 'Cause you took her back
to your place.</b></Default>

00:13:54.039 --> 00:13:56.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, I didn't.
- But you guys left together!</b></Default>

00:13:56.590 --> 00:13:59.129 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- And went home separately.</b></Default>

00:13:59.210 --> 00:14:01.549 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, man, I was hopin'
for a juicier story.</b></Default>

00:14:01.629 --> 00:14:04.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How was the karaoke
at the after party?</b></Default>

00:14:04.139 --> 00:14:06.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Touko Kirishima's songs
were popular.</b></Default>

00:14:06.549 --> 00:14:08.509 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone sang so well, too.</b></Default>

00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:11.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Touko Kirishima
is still popular, huh?</b></Default>

00:14:11.100 --> 00:14:12.809 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you mean
by "still popular?"</b></Default>

00:14:12.889 --> 00:14:14.309 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's in her prime right now.</b></Default>

00:14:14.690 --> 00:14:15.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- See, look.</b></Default>

00:14:15.690 --> 00:14:18.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [singing in Japanese]</b></Default>

00:14:18.820 --> 00:14:20.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- This song
is Touko Kirishima's.</b></Default>

00:14:21.240 --> 00:14:23.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So Touko Kirishima
is the one singing?</b></Default>

00:14:23.820 --> 00:14:25.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nah, she's a faceless beauty
for the ad.</b></Default>

00:14:25.909 --> 00:14:27.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's, like, a cover song?</b></Default>

00:14:27.279 --> 00:14:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So Touko Kirishima's
true identity is unknown.</b></Default>

00:14:30.580 --> 00:14:33.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yep. Oh, but there's sort of
a rumor goin' around</b></Default>

00:14:33.539 --> 00:14:36.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that it might be Mai Sakurajima.
So what do you think?</b></Default>

00:14:36.539 --> 00:14:39.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could your girlfriend actually
be Touko Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:14:39.129 --> 00:14:40.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Absolutely not.</b></Default>

00:14:40.799 --> 00:14:43.549 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Finally found you.
- Want something?</b></Default>

00:14:43.629 --> 00:14:45.429 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm gonna borrow Sakuta
for a bit.</b></Default>

00:14:45.509 --> 00:14:47.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, do with him as you wish?</b></Default>

00:14:47.950 --> 00:14:49.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:14:51.600 --> 00:14:53.389 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did you see Uzuki today?</b></Default>

00:14:53.480 --> 00:14:55.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I did.
We had Spanish together.</b></Default>

00:14:56.399 --> 00:14:57.559 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- How did she seem?</b></Default>

00:14:57.940 --> 00:14:58.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Pretty normal.</b></Default>

00:14:59.070 --> 00:15:00.399 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing stood out as strange.</b></Default>

00:15:00.820 --> 00:15:02.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did she say anything about me?</b></Default>

00:15:02.529 --> 00:15:03.529 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Not really.</b></Default>

00:15:03.779 --> 00:15:05.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nothing about Sweet Bullet?</b></Default>

00:15:05.570 --> 00:15:07.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She did mention that you guys
have a gig next week.</b></Default>

00:15:07.909 --> 00:15:09.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Is that it?</b></Default>

00:15:09.120 --> 00:15:10.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, is there something
I should know?</b></Default>

00:15:11.700 --> 00:15:13.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- We had a fight yesterday.</b></Default>

00:15:13.830 --> 00:15:15.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I was just wondering.</b></Default>

00:15:15.750 --> 00:15:17.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- So, what was the fight over?</b></Default>

00:15:17.460 --> 00:15:19.919 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, lately we've all been
talking with our agency</b></Default>

00:15:20.000 --> 00:15:22.259 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about our future together
as an idol group.</b></Default>

00:15:22.340 --> 00:15:24.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Do you mean like whether
or not you guys</b></Default>

00:15:24.470 --> 00:15:26.799 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are gonna keep going
or disband altogether?</b></Default>

00:15:27.139 --> 00:15:28.389 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm-hmm.
- But I thought you</b></Default>

00:15:28.470 --> 00:15:30.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were gaining fans
and getting more work.</b></Default>

00:15:30.970 --> 00:15:34.389 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, so we were discussing</b></Default>

00:15:34.889 --> 00:15:37.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uzuki especially has
a lot of work offers</b></Default>

00:15:37.350 --> 00:15:39.899 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the agency is thinking about
all sorts of things.</b></Default>

00:15:39.980 --> 00:15:41.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Like what?</b></Default>

00:15:41.360 --> 00:15:43.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Like Uzuki going solo.</b></Default>

00:15:43.649 --> 00:15:46.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just yesterday I overheard
our manager talking</b></Default>

00:15:46.570 --> 00:15:48.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to someone about it on
the phone.</b></Default>

00:15:48.279 --> 00:15:50.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Does Hirokawa know about that?</b></Default>

00:15:50.700 --> 00:15:52.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't think so.</b></Default>

00:15:53.240 --> 00:15:55.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What do you want, Toyohama?</b></Default>

00:15:55.620 --> 00:15:56.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, I, uh...</b></Default>

00:15:57.370 --> 00:15:59.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I still wanna stand
with everyone as Sweet Bullet</b></Default>

00:15:59.789 --> 00:16:01.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and perform on
the Budokan stage.</b></Default>

00:16:02.299 --> 00:16:03.879 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But more than anything else</b></Default>

00:16:03.960 --> 00:16:07.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want all of the group members
to be rewarded for their\Nefforts.</b></Default>

00:16:07.340 --> 00:16:09.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uzuki's been working harder
than anyone.</b></Default>

00:16:09.679 --> 00:16:11.139 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, I see now.</b></Default>

00:16:11.220 --> 00:16:13.809 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you beat around the bush
to try telling her that</b></Default>

00:16:13.889 --> 00:16:15.519 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she wasn't getting it at
all.</b></Default>

00:16:15.600 --> 00:16:17.389 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that made you
get all worked up</b></Default>

00:16:17.480 --> 00:16:20.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and flustered so it ended up
sounding like an argument?</b></Default>

00:16:20.610 --> 00:16:22.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, basically.
- Man.</b></Default>

00:16:22.399 --> 00:16:24.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Talk about your
first world problem.</b></Default>

00:16:24.279 --> 00:16:26.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So basically you've
been working more</b></Default>

00:16:26.399 --> 00:16:27.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and are complaining
because things aren't</b></Default>

00:16:28.029 --> 00:16:29.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like what they used to be?</b></Default>

00:16:29.570 --> 00:16:30.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you talk to Mai about this</b></Default>

00:16:30.990 --> 00:16:32.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she'd smack you
for real this time.</b></Default>

00:16:32.659 --> 00:16:33.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

00:16:34.580 --> 00:16:37.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If it isn't
Mr. Super Popular Azusagawa!</b></Default>

00:16:37.460 --> 00:16:39.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I told you I'm
not super popular.</b></Default>

00:16:39.210 --> 00:16:40.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But what do you want, Fukuyama?</b></Default>

00:16:40.830 --> 00:16:43.379 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You think you could introduce
me to some cute girls, dude?</b></Default>

00:16:43.460 --> 00:16:46.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What about the girl you
swapped Ids with the other day?</b></Default>

00:16:46.169 --> 00:16:47.509 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, she ghosted me.</b></Default>

00:16:47.840 --> 00:16:49.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- My condolences.</b></Default>

00:16:49.590 --> 00:16:51.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Look, I'd even be happy
with Toyohama.</b></Default>

00:16:51.799 --> 00:16:53.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She'd be pissed
if she heard you say "even."</b></Default>

00:16:54.059 --> 00:16:55.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Toyohama has a short fuse.</b></Default>

00:16:56.389 --> 00:16:57.809 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, hey</b></Default>

00:16:57.889 --> 00:16:59.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I gotta prep for work first.</b></Default>

00:17:02.690 --> 00:17:05.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unfortunately, today's topic
is a bit troublesome.</b></Default>

00:17:09.900 --> 00:17:12.819 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[dramatic piano music]</b></Default>

00:17:12.910 --> 00:17:14.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

00:17:14.240 --> 00:17:15.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm? Hmm?</b></Default>

00:17:21.579 --> 00:17:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe there's a club
that studies Santa Claus</b></Default>

00:17:24.000 --> 00:17:25.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at this school?</b></Default>

00:17:26.670 --> 00:17:27.589 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[punch card clicks]</b></Default>

00:17:27.670 --> 00:17:28.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]</b></Default>

00:17:29.420 --> 00:17:30.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]
[gasps]</b></Default>

00:17:30.839 --> 00:17:32.009 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hello, there.</b></Default>

00:17:32.089 --> 00:17:33.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Kaede? You're here?</b></Default>

00:17:33.470 --> 00:17:35.349 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wasn't Sakuta supposed
to be working now?</b></Default>

00:17:35.430 --> 00:17:37.809 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Big brother is over at
the cram school today.</b></Default>

00:17:42.140 --> 00:17:43.309 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Um, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:17:43.400 --> 00:17:45.359 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's wrong?
- I don't get it.</b></Default>

00:17:45.690 --> 00:17:47.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Something not clicking
for you?</b></Default>

00:17:47.230 --> 00:17:49.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I don't know how to get
a cute girlfriend.</b></Default>

00:17:49.240 --> 00:17:50.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you explain?</b></Default>

00:17:50.490 --> 00:17:52.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Let's solve test problems
during class.</b></Default>

00:17:52.569 --> 00:17:55.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Come on! You have the cutest
girlfriend in the world!</b></Default>

00:17:55.119 --> 00:17:56.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can't you give me some pointers?
- Actually, I have</b></Default>

00:17:56.910 --> 00:17:58.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the cutest girlfriend in
the universe</b></Default>

00:17:58.539 --> 00:18:00.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but that still doesn't mean I
can help you.</b></Default>

00:18:00.410 --> 00:18:02.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- The entire reason I asked
to be in your class</b></Default>

00:18:02.579 --> 00:18:04.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the first place was because
I thought you'd tell me</b></Default>

00:18:04.750 --> 00:18:06.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a foolproof way of getting
a girlfriend.</b></Default>

00:18:06.750 --> 00:18:09.339 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew I should have applied
to Ms. Futaba's class.</b></Default>

00:18:09.420 --> 00:18:11.799 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's got a way bigger brain
than you do, anyway.</b></Default>

00:18:12.130 --> 00:18:13.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And big boobs!</b></Default>

00:18:13.630 --> 00:18:16.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That last statement
will get you hated by girls</b></Default>

00:18:16.140 --> 00:18:18.309 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you should be careful.
- [exhales sharply]</b></Default>

00:18:18.930 --> 00:18:21.099 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm doing my job seriously.</b></Default>

00:18:21.180 --> 00:18:24.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I heard a word
that makes me think otherwise.</b></Default>

00:18:24.309 --> 00:18:25.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I wasn't the one that said it.</b></Default>

00:18:25.859 --> 00:18:27.359 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- By the way</b></Default>

00:18:27.440 --> 00:18:29.609 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got a text
from Kunimi earlier.</b></Default>

00:18:29.690 --> 00:18:31.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- About what?
- He let me know he got through</b></Default>

00:18:31.819 --> 00:18:34.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the end of his firefighter
training with no hitches</b></Default>

00:18:34.529 --> 00:18:37.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and said feel at ease because
he's been assigned to a station.</b></Default>

00:18:37.779 --> 00:18:39.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- He says that like
there's actually something</b></Default>

00:18:39.450 --> 00:18:40.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to worry about.</b></Default>

00:18:40.750 --> 00:18:42.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- His work's going
to be starting up next week.</b></Default>

00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:44.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So he invited us out
for some tea</b></Default>

00:18:44.829 --> 00:18:46.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after things settle down.</b></Default>

00:18:46.170 --> 00:18:48.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, Kunimi's treat
from his first paycheck?</b></Default>

00:18:48.500 --> 00:18:50.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That's what I figured
you would say</b></Default>

00:18:50.339 --> 00:18:52.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I already
replied accordingly.</b></Default>

00:18:52.759 --> 00:18:55.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>OCTOBER 4TH
[birds chirping]</b></Default>

00:18:55.220 --> 00:18:56.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Good morning!
- Hey.</b></Default>

00:18:56.759 --> 00:18:58.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I warmed up your seat
for you while I waited</b></Default>

00:18:58.720 --> 00:18:59.849 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for you to show up.</b></Default>

00:19:01.599 --> 00:19:02.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah--</b></Default>

00:19:04.099 --> 00:19:07.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, do you actually hate me
or something?</b></Default>

00:19:07.359 --> 00:19:10.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sitting in a chair
is way better when it's cold.</b></Default>

00:19:10.109 --> 00:19:11.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, same for beer.</b></Default>

00:19:11.779 --> 00:19:13.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You got the homework?
- Yeah, of course.</b></Default>

00:19:13.359 --> 00:19:14.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Mm-hmm.
- That's good.</b></Default>

00:19:14.359 --> 00:19:16.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uzuki?
- I did 'em just fine!</b></Default>

00:19:16.700 --> 00:19:18.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh?
- I fell asleep during.</b></Default>

00:19:18.819 --> 00:19:21.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all giggling]
- Would you all pardon me a sec?</b></Default>

00:19:21.119 --> 00:19:22.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all: Mm...</b></Default>

00:19:22.119 --> 00:19:24.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps approaching]</b></Default>

00:19:25.920 --> 00:19:27.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did Nodoka say something?</b></Default>

00:19:27.710 --> 00:19:30.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What something?
- Something is something.</b></Default>

00:19:30.289 --> 00:19:31.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's up with that?</b></Default>

00:19:31.500 --> 00:19:33.799 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did something happen
with Toyohama yesterday?</b></Default>

00:19:33.880 --> 00:19:36.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I was in a photo shoot
so I haven't seen her.</b></Default>

00:19:36.509 --> 00:19:38.799 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although, she pinged me earlier
and asked</b></Default>

00:19:38.890 --> 00:19:40.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Are you on campus now?"
- And?</b></Default>

00:19:41.009 --> 00:19:43.349 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- If she's making an effort
to ask something like that</b></Default>

00:19:43.430 --> 00:19:45.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>don't you think she might have
something to talk to me about?</b></Default>

00:19:46.059 --> 00:19:48.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Maybe there are people
that don't think so.</b></Default>

00:19:48.349 --> 00:19:51.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did something happen
to you yesterday, though?</b></Default>

00:19:51.109 --> 00:19:52.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Something like what?</b></Default>

00:19:52.529 --> 00:19:53.779 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Something is something.</b></Default>

00:19:53.859 --> 00:19:55.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, you copied me!</b></Default>

00:19:55.569 --> 00:19:57.069 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm feeling really good today.</b></Default>

00:19:57.410 --> 00:19:59.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like I'm finally on
the same wavelength</b></Default>

00:19:59.119 --> 00:20:01.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as everyone else.
[giggles]</b></Default>

00:20:03.200 --> 00:20:04.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- What's for lunch today?</b></Default>

00:20:05.039 --> 00:20:06.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Cafeteria trip?
- [grunts]</b></Default>

00:20:06.369 --> 00:20:09.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go!
[all speaking at once]</b></Default>

00:20:09.130 --> 00:20:11.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Azusagawa, have you got
any lunch plans?</b></Default>

00:20:11.630 --> 00:20:13.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I made my own lunch box
for today.</b></Default>

00:20:13.710 --> 00:20:14.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Did you make me one?</b></Default>

00:20:14.960 --> 00:20:16.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- That would be weird.</b></Default>

00:20:16.130 --> 00:20:18.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, true.
I'd get creeped out.</b></Default>

00:20:18.470 --> 00:20:21.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[tense music]</b></Default>

00:20:21.470 --> 00:20:28.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪ ♪</b></Default>

00:20:30.940 --> 00:20:31.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uzuki!</b></Default>

00:20:32.059 --> 00:20:33.319 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasping]</b></Default>

00:20:33.819 --> 00:20:36.069 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Sorry, can you girls
go on ahead without me?</b></Default>

00:20:36.150 --> 00:20:37.359 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all grunting]
- Sure.</b></Default>

00:20:37.450 --> 00:20:38.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Okay.</b></Default>

00:20:48.660 --> 00:20:49.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- All right.</b></Default>

00:20:50.500 --> 00:20:52.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I'll go buy myself
a drink.</b></Default>

00:20:52.420 --> 00:20:53.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- You can have this.</b></Default>

00:20:54.380 --> 00:20:55.589 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]</b></Default>

00:20:55.670 --> 00:20:57.589 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Hey, um, Nodoka, you wanted</b></Default>

00:20:57.670 --> 00:20:58.839 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to talk about the other day</b></Default>

00:20:58.920 --> 00:21:02.009 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>didn't you?
I am so, so sorry!</b></Default>

00:21:02.089 --> 00:21:04.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't really understand
how everyone else was feeling.</b></Default>

00:21:05.099 --> 00:21:07.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's only natural
for you to be feeling upset.</b></Default>

00:21:08.059 --> 00:21:09.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uzuki.
- We're talking on a lot more</b></Default>

00:21:10.019 --> 00:21:12.809 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>solo work now so we have less
time for activities as a group.</b></Default>

00:21:13.400 --> 00:21:14.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I don't want that, either</b></Default>

00:21:14.859 --> 00:21:17.359 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so all of us really need
to talk it out together.</b></Default>

00:21:19.109 --> 00:21:20.279 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- I'm sorry.</b></Default>

00:21:20.359 --> 00:21:22.109 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I said way too much.</b></Default>

00:21:22.200 --> 00:21:23.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, you didn't!</b></Default>

00:21:23.740 --> 00:21:25.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I only realized it because
of you.</b></Default>

00:21:26.490 --> 00:21:28.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [grunts]
- Honestly, solo work</b></Default>

00:21:28.160 --> 00:21:29.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is important, too, you know.</b></Default>

00:21:29.619 --> 00:21:31.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But still, it just doesn't
mean anything</b></Default>

00:21:31.750 --> 00:21:33.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if we're all split apart because
of it.</b></Default>

00:21:34.079 --> 00:21:35.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- [groans]
- We can do this</b></Default>

00:21:35.630 --> 00:21:37.089 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if we all work together.</b></Default>

00:21:37.170 --> 00:21:38.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everybody's gonna be there</b></Default>

00:21:38.460 --> 00:21:40.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for today's dance lesson</b></Default>

00:21:41.339 --> 00:21:43.839 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uh, yeah.
I think we should be.</b></Default>

00:21:44.180 --> 00:21:47.349 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nodoka, I'm not saying
something off base, am I?</b></Default>

00:21:47.430 --> 00:21:50.849 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- No, um, that's exactly what
I wanted to talk about.</b></Default>

00:21:50.940 --> 00:21:52.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, that's good to hear.</b></Default>

00:21:52.769 --> 00:21:54.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.</b></Default>

00:21:54.099 --> 00:21:55.269 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Nodoka?</b></Default>

00:21:55.609 --> 00:21:56.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Oh, it's nothing.</b></Default>

00:21:56.859 --> 00:21:58.359 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's all talk it out.</b></Default>

00:21:58.440 --> 00:22:00.359 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll start getting in touch
with everyone.</b></Default>

00:22:00.440 --> 00:22:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, please do!</b></Default>

00:22:02.029 --> 00:22:04.319 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, well, my friends
are waiting at the cafeteria</b></Default>

00:22:04.410 --> 00:22:06.029 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I gotta go.
