00:22:06.119 --> 00:22:07.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

00:22:13.960 --> 00:22:16.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Was that really Uzuki?</b></Default>

00:22:18.000 --> 00:22:20.759 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She was gauging my feelings
as she talked.</b></Default>

00:22:20.839 --> 00:22:22.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not like her at all.</b></Default>

00:22:22.799 --> 00:22:24.299 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah, it's not.</b></Default>

00:22:24.799 --> 00:22:27.049 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Uzuki was reading the room.</b></Default>

00:22:27.140 --> 00:22:28.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- She was.</b></Default>

00:22:29.140 --> 00:22:33.019 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Then maybe it's like with me
and my big sister.</b></Default>

00:22:33.519 --> 00:22:35.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Are you saying she swapped
