00:22:35.769 --> 00:22:37.769 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Yeah.
- Okay, then let's say it is</b></Default>

00:22:37.859 --> 00:22:39.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>some sort of puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

00:22:40.190 --> 00:22:41.529 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that a bad thing?</b></Default>

00:22:42.029 --> 00:22:43.609 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- It's not bad</b></Default>

00:22:44.109 --> 00:22:45.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean...</b></Default>

00:22:45.410 --> 00:22:46.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think it's okay?</b></Default>

00:22:47.410 --> 00:22:49.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>- Well, let's just give
it until tomorrow and see</b></Default>

00:22:49.950 --> 00:22:51.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if she's back to normal by then.</b></Default>

